```

## Fix 6: Request ID validation to prevent log injection
File: packages/elysia-plugins/src/request-id.ts

Validate that incoming x-request-id matches UUID format before trusting it:
```typescript
const UUID_RE = /^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{12}$/i
const incoming = headers['x-request-id']
const id = incoming && UUID_RE.test(incoming) ? incoming : crypto.randomUUID()
```

